{"body": "Could you be a bit more specific about the reason why button_to_function should be deprecated?\n\nTo be a bit more specific, I have following code:\n\nview:\n```erb\n<%= form_tag('/products', method: 'post', remote: true) do %>\n    <div id=\"product_errors\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n    <%= button_to_function 'Add field', \"$.addField($('#mongoField').val());\"%>\n    <%= text_field_tag 'mongoField', 'pcode' %>\n    <div id=\"mongoFields\"></div>\n    <br/>\n    <%= submit_tag 'Add/update' %>\n<% end %>\n```\ncustom.js:\n```ruby\n$.addField = function(field) {\n    $('#mongoFields').append('\\\n        <br />\\\n        <label for=\"product_' + field + '\">' + field + '</label>\\\n        <input id=\"product_' + field + '\" name=\"product[' + field + ']\" type=\"text\" value=\"\" />'\n    );\n};\n```\n\nThe button_to_function call adds a new input field to the form representing customized database record bound to be saved into MongoDB.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6472984", "created_at": "2012-06-21T02:50:11Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/5922#issuecomment-6472984", "updated_at": "2012-06-21T02:59:35Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 5922, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Valafar/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Valafar/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Valafar/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/Valafar", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Valafar/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/Valafar", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Valafar/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/34436f111b64abfb90c9b8d8682c73a1?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Ffe3bb18804ad9cdad6df3b84d5462aad.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Valafar/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/Valafar/received_events", "gravatar_id":